Alas, it's Chepauk. The ball sticks in the pitch, doesn't come on, and eventually takes the inside-half and tamely balloons over to mid-on. de Kock c Henriques b Hooda 3(5)

Commentary Text: Rahul Chahar to Mayank, out Caught by Suryakumar Yadav!! Chahar provides the much needed breakthrough for Mumbai Indians. A needless shot from Agarwal and he throws away yet another start. Tossed up and drifted into the right hander, Agarwal wanted to go over long-on and even cleared his front leg to free his arms, but the ball turned to make it a miscue and SKY makes no mistake running in from long-on.
